<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٢٩٦ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5178">قَبِيصَةُ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2472">سُفْيَانُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3644">عَبْدِ اللهِ بْنِ دِينَارٍ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3807">ابْنِ عُمَرَ </a><span class="special">﵄</span> قَالَ: سَمِعْتُ النَّبِيَّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> يَقُولُ: <span class="c2">«الْفِتْنَةُ مِنْ هُنَا وَأَشَارَ إِلَى الْمَشْرِقِ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>